node.text: I screamed when I saw it in the magazine!!! All I could think was yes apricot tea❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️

look, ma! I’m in @glamourmag! ✨ I’ve been waiting to announce this until I could get my hands on a physical copy, but I’m too excited & it’s also too cold outside to try to go out & find one, so I’m just going to use this digitized version as proof. ➖ whenever I end up in print it’s a huge honor, but this one is particularly special because it’s the last ever print issue of Glamour (they’re going digital after this). so it’s pretty monumental, especially to have my work highlighted in this way alongside @freeandnative & @alexiwasser (who I used to follow way way back during my fashion blogging days). big love + thanks go to @mollyoswaks for making this happen & to my client, Kait, who spoke so highly of her experience working with me. & shoutout to @extracelestial who shot this photo of me in her tiny kitchen last year!!!!➖ the full feature is out now in their January issue. 💖
So cool! And deserving. You articulate yourself very well
@evyan.whitney congrats!! Cheers to more sexual liberation for all!
This is amazing!! It warms my heart and lights my spirit to see individuals like you, and your work being praised in the mainstream!! ❤️💛💜🖤
@wordtowhomadeya411 I think so? I’ve admittedly had a really tough time finding it in stores like Walgreens, so I’d call before you go searching. book stores seem to have it though!
@a_d_mitchell thank you so much. that means a lot. 🌹🌹🌹
Let me tell you something about your podcast?!?!?!?!?! Whoooooo chillllllle. I listened to 5 episodes today, personally identifying in some way to each. You are doing GOOD WORK.
@zaddyopolis thanks honey! it’s good to see you comment here 💞💞 I hope you’re doing well!
omg! congratulations! i don’t know how to explain how happy this makes me — you’re amazing! ❤️❤️❤️
🙌🏽 Congratulations!!! Been following since the fashion blog days ☺️ and this is so exciting to see!
What a big thing!!! So exciting Congrats!
Wow, that’s a huge achievement!! Congrats 😁😁
Give this beautiful human her blue check mark! @instagram
@manokriti if you have an inquiry, please email me directly. link is in bio. thanks!
